{
  "stem": "24111.7",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in-- in-- oh, I should say we-- were in a terrible mental stage, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because, first of all, we felt we were in-- we saved ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we left-- in my case, I left my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left all my friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I left small children still in Italy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to believe that when Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lichtheim told me the money went to the frontier and went into Chichibo's hands, I had to believe that Chichibo would be-- Chichibo would be able to go back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But all those things, sitting in-- in Busserach, I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learn from that later on when my mother came and Joschko and the children came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in-- in those days of uncertainty, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was under terrible mental pressure, not only me, our little group.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, the Swiss in Busserach, that was a military-run camp, extremely strict.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The food supply was completely limited to a quarter-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] quarter-pound triangle of cheese and potatoes boiled in water.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'll tell you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the time I crossed the border, the Italian military [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] disintegrated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't want to fight the war anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And hundreds of soldiers, from officer rank down to the lowest soldier, tried to escape Italy and the-- and the possibility that they had to fight under German command still in the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they-- they escaped to-- to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the tragic part of the whole is that the Swiss accepted them more readily than the Jewish refugees, just because they had a uniform on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our camp in Busserach, most [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] people were actually ex-Italian soldiers, coming at the same time I came over the border, perhaps in different locations, into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
